songs.title: From The Distance To Valentina
songs.lyrics:
Let's do this fun
Leave the gun
Leave the knife
Wherever you are
Wherever you listen to me
If you are away far
I remind you that you do not have to fall
On your face, in your arms
There are the memories
There are the expieriences
Do not tell anyone
I will always be your fan
Far, so far babe, yeah, aye aye
